data.description: Welcome to this charming Spanish style 3Bedroom/2Bath Bungalow Home located in the heart of Umatilla Florida. This lovely property offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for those seeking a peaceful retreat in a friendly neighborhood. Home features well appointed living area with wood burning fireplace and is ideal for both relaxation and entertainment and has the original hardwood floors as well as the traditional classic moldings and millwork throughout.  Dining room offers the perfect spot for casual dinners with family and friends and the kitchen features all newer stainless appliances, double basin sink and pantry closet. The master/primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, featuring wood burning fireplace and an en-suite bathroom with separate soaking tub, shower and double vanities for added comfort and privacy. This bungalow home also features a 3rd bedroom/home office which has a separate entrance and could be used for a day/reading porch or even a playroom, having a separate entrance really makes for a very flexible space depending on your families needs. Additionally includes an inside laundry room for convenience. Nicely situated on a corner lot, oversized gravel parking pad/driveway. In addition to its charming interior and exterior features, this home benefits from a prime location in Umatilla. You'll be just a short distance from local parks, shopping, dining,  and entertainment options, as well as convenient access to major roadways for easy commuting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm of this Umatilla gem!
